<br>
What direction do you think Povar is heading? I see more and more high level guilds... I mean I think there are more of those now than the smaller family/roleplaying type. Even when one falls, seems like three more pop up to replace it. Anyone else thinks it's getting way too crowded? <br>
<br>
With new games like EQ2 and SWG coming out, do you think we will see a decline in our server population? I personally don't think we will. I think most people will say that they have put too much time in here to just up and leave and start over hehe. If I ever decide to &quot;quit&quot; EQ, I'm most definitely going back to playing Tetris anyways... maybe even some old skool Mario! =) Bowser tells you, &quot;Oh god not you again..&quot;<br>
<br>
I'm not playing for a few months due to skool and other things in RL, so I'm kinda looking forward to see what will change in those months that I'm not there to watch it firsthand.<br>
<br>
Feel free to post on anything you think is going to happen on Povar, or would like to see happen on Povar. This has been called the greatest of the servers, let's keep that reputation hehe.<br>
<br>
Peace.<br>
<br>
